{"tid":868550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歷史文件] 1993, 1998, 2001年啟德填海計劃","createTime":"2018-10-19T14:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T14:35:21.000Z","uid":32934,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a6afb2932b322172fc6c786bfa2433f1f7efa078","tid":868550,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:35:21.000Z","msg":"細細個幾留意香港發展, 果陣小學, 我已經知有東涌線, 沙中線, 將軍澳線, 北港先線, 南港島線,<br />\n仲有竹篙灣貨櫃碼頭, 西區填海, 之後仲有就係呢份...啟德填海<br />\n當時覺得好正, 但依家慶幸冇填, 如果唔係就真係變維多利亞河...<br />\n但2001年既計劃係最可取, 最主要係利用到土瓜灣個三角位, 同埋觀塘停機坪同跑道分隔既問題<br />\n依家搭的士入去啟德跑道好貴...又唔可以將d土地發展得好少少.<br />\n<br />\n1993<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pland.gov.hk/pland_en/p_study/prog_s/sek_09/website_chib5_eng/pdf/SEKD_DC_1993_EXESUM.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pland.gov.hk%2Fpland_en%2Fp_study%2Fprog_s%2Fsek_09%2Fwebsite_chib5_eng%2Fpdf%2FSEKD_DC_1993_EXESUM.pdf&d=BpnPxQCMLZFFl5rQmDXvrW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=fedb2eb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pland.gov.hk/pland_en/p_study/prog_s/sek_09/website_chib5_eng/pdf/SEKD_DC_1993_EXESUM.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n1998<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pland.gov.hk/pland_en/p_study/prog_s/sek_09/website_chib5_eng/pdf/FS_SEKD_ExeSum1998_Chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pland.gov.hk%2Fpland_en%2Fp_study%2Fprog_s%2Fsek_09%2Fwebsite_chib5_eng%2Fpdf%2FFS_SEKD_ExeSum1998_Chi.pdf&d=BpnPxQCMLZFFl5rQmDXvrW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=103dadab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pland.gov.hk/pland_en/p_study/prog_s/sek_09/website_chib5_eng/pdf/FS_SEKD_ExeSum1998_Chi.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2001<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pland.gov.hk/pland_en/p_study/prog_s/sek_09/website_chib5_eng/pdf/SEKD_CFS_2001_EXESUM_CHI.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pland.gov.hk%2Fpland_en%2Fp_study%2Fprog_s%2Fsek_09%2Fwebsite_chib5_eng%2Fpdf%2FSEKD_CFS_2001_EXESUM_CHI.pdf&d=BpnPxQCMLZFFl5rQmDXvrW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9bf34b1e\" d